column5: Out on quinte good start to the day couple jumbos pretty slow so far.
A day on the ice is better then a day at work. Nice looking Jumbos
Twenty keepers just enough action to keep us busy.... back at it tomorrow.  I would kill for bacon wrapped perch....
Here's a couple more from yesterday, I knew the area was good for walleye but there were some giant perch around like this hog...
Jeeze that perch is huge, nice work.
Wow, that perch is a hog. I had a buddy who went out today who said the walleye were slow.
